query: SELECT MIN(cn1.name) AS first_company, MIN(cn2.name) AS second_company, MIN(mi_idx1.info) AS first_rating, MIN(mi_idx2.info) AS second_rating, MIN(t1.title) AS first_movie, MIN(t2.title) AS second_movie FROM company_name AS cn1, company_name AS cn2, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, kind_type AS kt1, kind_type AS kt2, link_type AS lt, movie_companies AS mc1, movie_companies AS mc2, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2, movie_link AS ml, title AS t1, title AS t2 WHERE lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND t1.id = ml.movie_id AND t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND cn2.id = mc2.company_id AND t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND (mc2.note like '%Italy%' OR mc2.note like '%Russia%' OR mc2.note like '%UK%' OR mc2.note like '%Japan%' OR mc2.note like '%India%') AND mi_idx1.info > '2.0' AND (t2.title like '%treasure%' OR t2.title like '%thunder%' OR t2.title like '%city%') AND (mc1.note like '%Australia%' OR mc1.note like '%Denmark%' OR mc1.note like '%Italy%') AND kt1.kind in ('tv mini series','movie','video movie','episode','tv movie','video game') AND it1.info in ('death date','LD dynamic range','portrayed in','LD color information','LD category','soundtrack','LD supplement','LD dialogue intellegibility','filming dates','votes distribution','other literature') AND mi_idx2.info > '10.0' AND t1.production_year < 2006 AND (t1.title like '%mission%' OR t1.title like '%pen%' OR t1.title like '%curse%') AND lt.link in ('followed by','spin off from','references','spoofs','remake of','follows','edited into','featured in','features','referenced in','unknown link','spoofed in','alternate language version of','similar to','remade as')
